User Stories

  This document describes the (initial) set of user stories as well as the
roles users have when using the Smart Reservation System (SRS).

* 1. Roles

  Describe the roles you have identified. I recommend to use a definition
list:

  [Customer] Person who books the resources. An ordinary user of the system.

  [Resource Manager] Person who manages the resources that can be booked.

  [System Admin] Admin of the system (and event. Product Owner).


